Package: scRNAtools
Title: Set of functions for the analysis of scRNASeq data
Version: 0.3
Authors@R: person("Laurent", "Modolo", email = "laurent.modolo@ens-lyon.fr",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package scRNASeq provides a set of function to perform quality
  control, classification, differential analysis and visualisation of scRNASeq
  data.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2), R6 (>= 2.2.1), e1071 (>= 1.6.8), base, ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1), grDevices, circlize, tximport, readr, plsgenomics, pCMF, ade4, SCnorm, sva, MASS, pscl, parallel, lme4, extraDistr, ComplexHeatmap, SIMLR, reshape2, mixtools, scran
